{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8fb06b3a-9fb7-49fa-9232-e8f3ca241b0e", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8fb06b3a-9fb7-49fa-9232-e8f3ca241b0e@1.pkg/1772597673068/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597673928", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8fb06b3a-9fb7-49fa-9232-e8f3ca241b0e@1.pkg/1772597673068/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597673928"}, "identifier": "8fb06b3a-9fb7-49fa-9232-e8f3ca241b0e", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查民法典的基本原则。</p>\n\n<p>A：诚信是民法典明文规定的基本原则，同时也是中华民族传统美德，故符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>B:民事活动既要遵守法律，也要遵循诚信等道德要求，题干中“诚信原则”本身即包含道德要求，说法错误.</p>\n\n<p>C:民法典将道德层面的诚信纳入法律，体现法律与道德相辅相成，共同规范社会秩序，符合题意。</p>\n\n<p>D:社会主义核心价值观包含“诚信”，民法典将其作为原则，体现了对社会公德的重视，故符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）民法典规定“民事主体从事民事活动，应当遵循诚信原则，秉持诚实，恪守承诺”。对此以下说法错误的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）民法典规定“民事主体从事民事活动，应当遵循诚信原则，秉持诚实，恪守承诺”。对此以下说法错误的是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8fb06b3a-9fb7-49fa-9232-e8f3ca241b0e@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755144133159", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>法律与道德相结合，共同维护社会秩序德</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>民事活动中只需遵守法律，无需考虑道德要求</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>诚信是民法典的基本原则，也是中华民族的传统美德</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>民法典注重融入社会主义核心价值观，彰显社会公德</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编）民法典规定“民事主体从事民事活动，应当遵循诚信原则，秉持诚实，恪守承诺”。对此以下说法错误的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "8fb06b3a-9fb7-49fa-9232-e8f3ca241b0e", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）民法典规定“民事主体从事民事活动，应当遵循诚信原则，秉持诚实，恪守承诺”。对此以下说法错误的是（     ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>（改编）民法典规定“民事主体从事民事活动，应当遵循诚信原则，秉持诚实，恪守承诺”。对此以下说法错误的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready",